Hugh Sheridan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hugh_Sheridan 0 Hugh Sheridan (born 30 June 1985) is an Australian actor, musician and television presenter who is known for his role as Ben Rafter in the television series Packed to the Rafters.
